org.orgName: District Court of the Third Judicial District of Washington Territory

body.p: In the District Court, Third Judicial District, holding terms at
In the matter of the application of C.F. Reed for Habeas Corpus
In the District Court holding terms at Seattle
In the matter of the application of C.F. Reed for Habeas Corpus } no. 5931

This cause coming on to be heard upon the Return of the Sheriff herein and the Court being sufficiently advised it is considered by the Court that said return is insufficient in Law and that said commitment under which the petitioner C.F. Reed is held is void and it is further considered by the Court that said C.F. Reed be and he is discharged from Custody and that he go hence without day
In the matter of the application of C.F. Reed for a Writ of Habeas Corpus
